    "body": "The method was (ec *Client) FilterLogs\r\nParams:\r\n\r\n```\r\nfromBlock := new(big.Int).SetInt64(rpc.PendingBlockNumber)\r\ntoBlock := fromBlock\r\ntopic := gthCrypto.Keccak256([]byte(\"MYEXAMPLETOPIC\"))\r\ntopics := []common.Hash{common.BytesToHash(topic)}\r\ntopicss := [][]common.Hash{topics}\r\n\r\ncontext.Background()\r\nq := FilterQuery{nil, fromBlock, toBlock, nil, topicss}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI'm not too concerned now with debugging my implementation since I got it working by setting \r\nfromBlock := new(big.Int).SetInt64(-1)\r\ntoBlock := fromBlock\r\n\r\nbut hopefully pointing out that PendingBlockNumber being different across modules will be useful and save others debugging time.",
